description.en:
Whadda The Conehead soldering kit

The Conehead is an audio circuit that imitates the chirping of a cricket. The cricket chirps depending on the light intensity.

Features
Printed circuit board with unique design
Chirps in the dark
Chirps depending on light intensity

Specifications:
Color: green
Gender: unisex
Target group: adults
Power supply: 3 V (CR2032 battery not included)
